1784407537406113	campaign_runtime	itc:v3:AWKfOZmeTnzMQAAAAAAAQb7tt677YAAAAAEsBw		item.comment	bn-2ja	{"body":"Completed capture/SIPp/secret/run-directory integration plus all mandatory independent-review regressions. Planner now uses versioned allowlisted case expectations with privacy rejection, exact lowercase enums/unique arrays, and minimal used-target BPF. Runtime now strictly revalidates the complete frozen plan; bounds plan and cancellable stdin sizes; retains PGIDs through leader exit; kills SIGTERM-ignoring descendants; redacts Authorization and configured secrets; enforces event-specific schema contracts, finite grace values, reserved fields, and a bounded LIFO rollback registry. Added campaign execute with collision-safe mode-0700 UTC run directories, immediate tcpdump readiness before OPTIONS preflight, preflight call gate, bounded capture/report teardown, SIPp/sipsak step adapter, env/FD/provider secret sources via stdin envelope, redacted command/event artifacts, executable hashes, timestamps/results/report, signal-safe preflight cleanup, and rootless ownership. Added real loopback UAS and container integration selftest. Verification: 42 campaign tests + 48 oracle tests pass; compileall, shell syntax, shellcheck pass; final image cc2ee3dbe666 passes tool smoke, legacy closed-loop SIP test, and real campaign selftest with 1 successful call, 9 captured SIP packets, and a complete report. Fixture secrets were scanned across argv/events/logs/artifacts. No external network traffic was sent."}	blake3:qVxcKfiszN7tClmaokI-gECejEcBbsW00_IFbA5y0S4
