1784407640249351	packet_oracle_schema	itc:v3:AWKSTMnnJJJM5kxAAAAAQara91VW7WAAAAE0Cw		item.comment	bn-lt3	{"body":"Post-completion adversarial hardening completed while implementing bn-3e3: relevant truncated/malformed/unknown/orphan/ambiguous signaling now blocks Known(True); physical snaplen truncation is tested through TShark; ACK completion binds exact INVITE CSeq/leg; offerless 2xx/ACK and reliable 183/PRACK offer-answer flows are modeled; failed re-INVITE restores confirmed; challenge To-tags do not fork; raw SDP line association handles no session c=, per-media c=, repeated codecs and leading attributes without serialization; changed RSeq/SDP is not a retransmission; Record-Route route-set and observed Route remain separate; BYE direction uses the full reversed flow. Full oracle suite passed after these fixes."}	blake3:tHZYJheQ1y3Drua6Ha3jBFBv_F1kQ6gs6Kpqo8keKus
1784407640268589	packet_oracle_schema	itc:v3:AWKSTMnnJJJM5kxAAAAAQara91VW7WAAAAE0DA		item.comment	bn-3e3	{"body":"Implemented RTP/RTCP correlation by active SDP revision, five-tuple, direction, SSRC and payload; exact/symmetric/unmatched correlation; RTCP sender mapping; RFC 3550 loss/duplicate/reorder/wrap/jitter metrics; timestamp continuity; and evidence-backed assertions for directionality, endpoints, payloads, codecs, DTMF, setup/pre-answer/post-BYE timing, sequence, jitter and renegotiation/SSRC transitions. Unknown and not-applicable semantics are explicit; encrypted media gets transport-only analysis. Tests cover good bidirectional media, one-way, third-party endpoints, mismatch, isolated timestamp jump, loss/dup/reorder, wrap, pre/post timing, renegotiated PT+SSRC, unexplained SSRC, symmetric RTP allow/deny, RTCP and SRTP unknowns. Verification: 51 oracle tests pass including generated real pcap/pcapng and physical truncation; schemas parse; existing selftest reconstructs and evaluates end to end."}	blake3:-QxKMr0XmafdIEK40mJGnE_7WdmHfMFexbEOTX_ulbs
