1784410280918378	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErfQ		item.comment	bn-sl8	{"body":"Implemented deterministic source-generated audio canary v1. Added integer-only seeded synthesis with direction-specific upward/downward chirp codes, calibrated silence, three amplitude steps, raw PCMU/PCMA/G.722 encoding and decoding, local marker recovery, strict manifest/hash verification, CC0 generated-artifact notice, docs, Make targets, and container packaging. Corpus: six one-second assets, 8,000 bytes each (48,000 payload bytes total), 20ms/160-byte packetization; G.722 correctly records 16kHz media and 8kHz RTP clock. Evidence: 8/8 focused tests pass; every asset decodes and all 18 markers recover, minimum installed-image correlation 0.999590; opposite-direction correlations stay below 0.40; silence, step levels, clipping, tamper rejection, exact hashes, and two-run byte determinism tested. Full repository discovery passed 83 tests. Host and image  are byte-identical. Image 7d3ecaa0a8721f4b281d2cf05f2e34a415a677996db27e8a237146714670908f rebuilt and smoke passed. No commit created."}	blake3:-1rnWBZeGzS_UYPFGo8Pwgy1thHD6cBiJ4amd6Yrd6w
