1784411372540477	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErowE		item.comment	bn-j8n	{"body":"Implemented privacy-safe one-dialog canonicalizer over oracle FrameRecord/Reconstruction. Requires exactly one complete unambiguous unencrypted leg and exactly one local endpoint; explicit codes/evidence diagnose incomplete, multi-leg/fork, ambiguity, encryption, and scope failures. Stable typed placeholders cover Call-ID/tags/contacts/branches/CSeq/lengths/signaling+media addresses/ports/SSRC/sequence/timestamps; absolute timing becomes relative windows; methods/responses/codecs/optional provisionals/teardown and source frames remain. Baseline, challenge, CANCEL, remote-BYE, and re-INVITE fixtures stable; raw IDs/addresses/Authorization absent. Verification: make learn-test -> 6/6 pass; compileall clean."}	blake3:R2D4zN_ZcxNUKQXnweQ0-5Mi5bqK5LEPHUl5e9cncQ0
