1784414060722448	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEryQE		item.comment	bn-224	{"body":"Implemented typed fusion of SIPp success/setup/timeout/5xx, packet-oracle verdicts, RTP loss/jitter, socket errors, and optional health facts. Added bounded deadline health adapters with typed missing/stale outcomes; required unknown data stops and is never treated as healthy. Conservative policy supports immediate hard stops, repeated soft thresholds, median-baseline adverse change points, streak reset/hysteresis, suspect states, monotonic level/time enforcement, and exact fact/rule/baseline/streak citations. Reports only tested healthy/degraded knee bounds, explicit ceiling censoring, and capacityClaim null. Added seeded stable, noisy, gradual, abrupt, hysteretic, change-point, unknown/stale, adapter, and censored tests plus operator docs/Make target. Evidence: focused 9/9 pass after final ordering hardening; full shared suite 199/199 pass; git diff check passes."}	blake3:gp4nAjIP_NHFpZdfndsA0Ge8qPtvw9oxNpa9XqgWQ40
