1784414483587954	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErzgE		item.comment	bn-3rf	{"body":"EXIT GATE PASS. Added tests/test_evidence_pack_exit_gate.py with six independent gates: (1) published sanitized sample reproducibility, moved-pack/no-source-workspace verification, clean reports-only CI scan; (2) mutation of every logical archive member payload and every path with canonical headers, all rejected; (3) exact otherwise-unused tar padding-byte tamper rejected distinctly by the optional signature boundary; (4) Authorization, Call-ID, and decoded-WAV fixture blocks default export, while explicit privacy acknowledgement still exports reports only and byte scans show no secret/identifier/audio leakage; (5) incomplete/interrupted run packs remain portable/verifiable after source deletion; (6) canonical identifier/time-origin equivalence plus codec/one-way/assertion regression corpus. Tightened verifier to require canonical member metadata/order and CI export to require embedded privacy pass unless --allow-privacy-findings is explicitly recorded. Published examples/evidence-pack/sanitized-evidence.tar (20,480 bytes, sha256 7ab4629c2f056e69b7e901ceb9b8410279163dc3830adc49fc9d30a23ed78b47) with deterministic generator/check and documentation. Documented integrity limit: unsigned self-contained verification authenticates logical members/identity but cannot externally authenticate unused tar padding; minisign covers exact archive bytes. Real image 449024c34b9f... probes passed: moved sample import/default export, actual minisign valid signature, real padding-byte signature failure with CLI exit 3, actual age recipient encrypt/decrypt/reverify, no plaintext temp residue, and privacy-blocked default CI export. Focused: 18 pack/gate/privacy + 31 learned all pass. Full: 210/210. Oracle: 79/79 plus 20k benchmark. Container build/smoke pass. No commits. Child only closed; manual parent goal intentionally left for root."}	blake3:swynu173-Y1la-9u9UuGGo-vL5140YN2o_Cigxktj