1784496878267206	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErugI		item.comment	bn-3kt	{"body":"Audit baseline (2026-07-19): first-class routes exist for workbench commands plus assert/media/envelope/resilience; exact container binary names remain reachable, but natural torture/chaos/ui forms fail with exit 127; --help fails with exit 2; capture/preflight/report/selftest/chaos-exit-gate remain sibling host scripts. The implementation must cover the complete registry, not only these sampled gaps, and all help/routing verification must remain network-free."}	blake3:j2WLGdxkpUm0XQfTXcAz-1VPuxI7V5IZsh1IMkJlvMs
