1784497559162727	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErxgI		item.comment	bn-3ug	{"body":"Completed unified host workflow routes for capture, preflight, report, selftest, and chaos-exit-gate. Added true no-action help for selftest/gate, a preflight --dry-run that skips resolution and traffic, automatic isolation for selftest, and portable runtime selection for the chaos gate. Dry-run and routing tests are green."}	blake3:AKgC3pb21L1fXCo1mAwyu-3tSXSh1zT8ell95dgVZ7I
1784497559186967	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErxwI		item.comment	bn-3b9	{"body":"Completed natural first-party aliases for campaign, torture, chaos, UI, evidence, pack, diff, media-echo, and all existing families. Direct execution preserves host paths; --isolated/--admin explicitly reuses packaged in-image targets; shell and -- COMMAND remain the expert escape hatches. Completeness test covers every sippycup-* binary."}	blake3:44Vy3QWbFQfD26OBkdKO3w7z3mQ_Q7-y1BqIOEbF-Vg
1784497559204186	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEryAI		item.comment	bn-3vq	{"body":"Completed offline help/discovery/version: global help, help COMMAND, COMMAND --help safety, version flag/command, activity and execution labels, deterministic typo suggestion, versioned commands JSON/schema, and registry-driven Bash completion. All public command help succeeds with the runtime set to a missing path."}	blake3:CDp8z44gVKZC1cMh9Ar6hgpGGvoe91-ltj8QV6rKLes
