1784497613880333	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEr0AI		item.comment	bn-31r	{"body":"Completed compatibility layer. Existing direct scripts and installed sippycup-* binaries remain callable; tests cover every legacy help path, fixed argv boundaries, container exit 23 propagation, SIGTERM propagation, clean JSON stdout, and recursion-free fixed targets. No deprecation warnings were added; docs define 1.x compatibility."}	blake3:bVbEVd2Sc_68nTFSCXPaK1wahselaxI49HwD8VKcTuA
1784497613903660	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEr0QI		item.comment	bn-dsc	{"body":"Completed public documentation migration. README, deep workflow guides, and evidence-pack example now use ./bin/sippycup for first-party operations; docs/CLI.md records host/container boundaries, safety labels, compatibility, escape hatch, and Bash completion. A repository test rejects reintroduction of sibling first-party spellings."}	blake3:GV05VjZSc3gyavz3IvCiJV_NTo_AJPOB1N6AGa_pyvk
