1784499927206928	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErjwM		item.comment	bn-371	{"body":"Completed the Phase 1 threat model and allowlist contract in docs/MCP-SECURITY.md. The boundary is local stdio, explicit public resources, ten typed offline/read-only tools, relative non-symlink work paths, structured bounded/redacted results, no network/capabilities, and explicit exclusion of shell, arbitrary argv/files, journals, raw payloads, authorization mutation, and all target-active workflows."}	blake3:YvMbQPYgh0yUr335zJ0zUpa7G63_cno5vOZFwtgdC9Q
