1784500256687660	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErlQM		item.comment	bn-7iz	{"body":"Implemented official mcp==1.27.2 SDK packaging, a stdio-only FastMCP adapter, bin/sippycup-mcp, unified 'sippycup mcp' routing, stock-client initialization/shutdown, protocol-only stdout, and actionable direct-host dependency errors. Real SDK interoperability passed in the prepared image."}	blake3:2cGE8Z3a3VxoYs6JmRjDdAP0B_K_mE6rsniOZ3PVF74
