1784500256755851	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErlwM		item.comment	bn-806	{"body":"Implemented canonical relative-path confinement with symlink rejection; one MiB structured-result/output limits; recursive secret-field and authorization-text redaction; two-call concurrency gate; 130-second fixed-helper deadline; deterministic environment; prlimit file ceilings; process-group kill on timeout; and MCP-specific 1,000-step planning caps. Focused timeout, traversal, symlink, redaction, output and DNS-offline tests pass."}	blake3:n7ZUDnavLU2NQr4uy0CbOy1Rl0Oazt41BG0amasqKy8
