1784500562828100	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErnwM		item.comment	bn-w23	{"body":"Completed the confined catalog: static catalog/commands/security resources plus allowlisted document and schema templates. Reads are name-mapped, regular-file-only, share-root-contained and capped at 2 MiB. Journals, work files, captures, credentials, run artifacts and arbitrary repository paths are excluded. Stock-client list/read checks pass."}	blake3:qVdIAQTJgszflFPAkxlZr1otHYOluipeGksbp1w25HU
