1784500562890371	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEroQM		item.comment	bn-mtv	{"body":"Completed ten typed Phase 1 tools: sandbox_status, doctor, rehearse_target, engagement_status, triage_capture, plan_campaign, plan_envelope, lint_evidence, verify_evidence_pack and run_torture_exit_gate. The real MCP exit gate called every tool against generated/copy-safe fixtures; all returned ok=true and validated against sippycup.dev/mcp-result/v1. No generic argv or live operation is registered."}	blake3:_elBa32nSQf_GHcb_ykKY3oOd2r7-Lz4lWxHr9xi1bQ
