1784500562953568	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErowM		item.comment	bn-ar2	{"body":"Completed container-offline routing through the unified launcher. The real Podman gate proved --network=none, cap-drop ALL, no NET_RAW/NET_ADMIN, raw socket denial, only loopback, no-new-privileges, pids limit, read-only root, read-only /work and bounded /tmp. --admin and --isolated broadening are rejected. Runtime selection remains Podman, nerdctl, then Docker."}	blake3:AWbvVXQkXyLfRDj4SCoo0Z1Y05SrSoDIZj7PCFtrVOI
