1784501450986031	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEr1QM		item.comment	bn-gno	{"body":"Completed the versioned offline WebRTC contract. Added strict Draft 2020-12 schemas for sippycup.dev/webrtc-scenario/v1 and webrtc-result/v1, standard-library semantic validators, network-free scenario/result fixtures, operator documentation, MCP resource discovery, image packaging, and 14 focused tests. Semantic validation rejects unknown fields, adapter capability mismatch, hostnames, public destinations in local_lab, non-loopback offline destinations, invalid target authorization windows, inline credential providers, secret-bearing output, inconsistent ceilings/counts/statuses, invalid typed unknowns, missing evidence, and non-monotonic events. V1 is audio-only, never retains raw audio, and cannot retain full SDP for approved targets. Validation: 14 WebRTC tests, 333 core tests, image smoke, pinned JSON Schema validation of both fixtures, MCP self-test, and 8-check MCP exit gate all passed. Image 362ece58086c1da524592457b9739e5a8f4c87ceed1a83e007c56ff16fd66c4d. No target traffic occurred."}	blake3:49Nf0e37hIUb77H3WRfeYrV3I6Lglh8EgWb9VFxG8Ek
