1784508690117185	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEr4QM		item.comment	bn-22j	{"body":"Implemented a socket-free WebRTC SDP parser, normalized transcript contract, offer/answer state-machine oracle, deterministic bounded single/pairwise negative generator, and failure-preserving minimizer. Coverage includes secure transport profiles, BUNDLE/mids, rtcp-mux, ICE options/end-of-candidates, hashed credentials and fingerprints, DTLS roles, codecs/RTCP feedback/extmaps, directions, glare, rollback, retry, renegotiation, and atomic two-sided ICE restarts. Raw SDP normalization is bounded and emits no raw credentials or fingerprint values. Integrated unified CLI, docs, fixtures, MCP discovery, and tests. Validation: make webrtc-test (36 Python plus Go test/vet), make cli-test (21), MCP tests (12), and full unittest discovery (358) pass; syntax, py_compile, and diff checks pass. No target traffic was generated."}	blake3:wDqnU6yt8BvciFO_G2wiBfZpIqrNyOoemsLfHxhsSwQ
