1784509025584775	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEr5QM		item.comment	bn-1k1	{"body":"Implemented the offline DTLS-SRTP identity and media-security oracle with strict policy/observation contracts. It verifies fingerprint binding and adapter verification, complementary roles, version/cipher agreement, downgrade rejection before media, SRTP profile agreement, opaque RTP/RTCP key separation, replay/auth rejection, RTP rollover and gaps, context-bound SSRCs, SRTCP protection/indexes, epoch/key reuse, rekey-to-context binding, two-sided rekey after observed ICE restart, failure closure, cleanup, and hard evidence ceilings. Reports explicitly state that session keys were not observed and make no capacity claim. Added fixtures, docs, unified CLI, MCP discovery, and regression tests. Validation: make webrtc-test (46 Python plus Go test/vet), make cli-test (22), MCP tests (12), and full unittest discovery (369) pass; syntax, py_compile, and diff checks pass. No target traffic was generated."}	blake3:sR-zrHb8J3F6G-OJNxP1bcxA_BtVQq4QUsNzBpCzL1M
