1784512699725074	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEr6QM		item.comment	bn-2r3	{"body":"Completed the offline cross-layer WebRTC call evidence oracle. It correlates stable signaling revisions, ordered ICE pair changes, DTLS associations, RTP and SRTCP streams/SSRCs, deterministic canary asset hashes, directional continuity and bounded round-trip latency, plus recovery across contiguous generations. Component failure and typed uncertainty remain distinct; encrypted/partial captures cannot pass. Strict privacy validation rejects credentials/tokens, raw candidates and literal addresses, browser/device metadata, raw audio, unknown fields, symlinks, and overlarge inputs. Published strict policy/evidence/report schemas, unified CLI route, MCP catalog resources, fixtures, docs, and tests. Validation: make webrtc-test (56 Python plus Go test/vet), make cli-test (23), MCP tests (12), full unittest discovery (380), JSON syntax, bash syntax, py_compile, and diff checks all pass. No target traffic was generated."}	blake3:jPIvSU46chJ0qQJRJ1KPuwbUiprJHBBYp1El4dOwtrQ
