1784514058540756	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEr8QM		item.comment	bn-3cr	{"body":"Milestone 7ef79a0 adds a real loopback-only TLS/RFC6455 signaling adapter and 12 browser-session checks: certificate validation, Origin/CSWSH boundary, authentication, expiry, replay, role authorization, size/rate ceilings, malformed transitions, disconnect, and reconnect. The fixed adapter exposes no URL/path/header/cookie/arbitrary message input, emits a strict normalized schema, and is packaged behind the no-network/capability-dropped optional container. Verification: 56 WebRTC Python tests, Go tests/vet, clean stdout/stderr, rebuilt image 62870ae7708d5b8d00ed261ba8a8c582eaa8fe350e0919027b77b4972594e90a, and container self-test pass. No target traffic. Remaining: Quad-specific protocol adapter and approval-bound target execution."}	blake3:TUelsb3maLmfAjWpPpN2rLhyYxmZEtxzu6Bm2jT4NDo
