1784556636670735	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEriAQ		item.comment	bn-2x2	{"body":"Implementation started after bn-3eb. Scope is a separate capability-backed tool layer: offline immutable preparation plus a narrowly allowlisted preflight adapter. External target traffic remains disabled; tests use no-network fakes or loopback only."}	blake3:9bFnEutsjJk5Ylf9lJ9SxnXX5cks-XGgZh72cnSh39M
1784557445937313	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEriQQ		item.comment	bn-2x2	{"body":"Implemented separate ./bin/sippycup mcp-live server with typed prepare_assessment and preflight_target tools. Preparation descriptor-pins and validates exact approved profile/plan/grant bytes, writes owner-private content-addressed mode-0400 snapshots, and sends no traffic. Preflight consumes an exact action/client/digest/literal-target/ceiling grant before a single fixed 2-second SIP OPTIONS adapter call; invalid/replayed/drifted inputs invoke the adapter zero times. Added strict trust/snapshot/result schemas, isolated bridge/cap-drop/read-only container launcher, redacted receipts/audit refs, docs, and tests. Known boundary is documented: current target restriction is application-layer, not a per-grant kernel egress ACL; that remains required for the live execution exit gate. Validation: focused MCP 29/29, CLI 25/25, full discovery 425/425, offline MCP interoperability exit gate pass, final container build and smoke pass. No target traffic was sent."}	blake3:kF0KrW13Zp1Z8_co1y3ms6oQ0qancdW11MMwmYZw23o
1784557445956262	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErigQ		item.move	bn-2x2	{"state":"done"}	blake3:sVj3U7iuOO7DQl9F0-OsWXARSeaJ79Bn9K6UoO0t_b0
